===Noun phrase===
'''[[derived]] [[function]]''' (''plural'' '''derived functions''')

{{analysis}} Of a function, another function, the value of which for any value of the [[independent variable]] is the [[instantaneous]] [[rate of change]] of the given function at that value of the independent variable.

====Synonyms====
*(''function''): [[derivative]]

